# Commands Used in Project

## Update System

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade -y
```

## Install Apache

```bash
sudo apt install apache2 -y
```

## Check Apache Status

```bash
sudo systemctl status apache2
```

## Navigate to Web Directory

```bash
cd /var/www/html
```

## List Files

```bash
ls
```

```bash
ls -la
```

## Change File Permissions

```bash
sudo chmod 777 index.html
```

## Edit HTML File

```bash
nano index.html
```

## Restart Apache

```bash
sudo systemctl restart apache2
```
